        <h1>Control Z</h1>
    
    <section id="overview" class="section">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>Control Z follows Sofia, a socially distant but sharp student, as she investigates a hacker exposing student's secrets at El Colegio Nacional, causing chaos, betrayals, and confrontations that test friendships, loyalty, and hidden pasts in the school.</p>
