    <section id="characters" class="section">
        <h2>Characters</h2>
        <ul>
            <li> Sofía Herrera --- A highly observant but socially distant student determined to uncover the hacker. </li>
            <li> Javier Williams --- A new student and former soccer star who befriends Sofía and helps her investigation. </li>
            <li> Raúl León --- A wealthy and charming student with a mysterious side, hiding secrets of his own. </li>
            <li> Natalia Alexander --- A popular girl obsessed with social status, whose life spirals due to financial problems. </li>
            <li> María Alexander --- Natalia’s sister, who struggles with self-esteem issues and a toxic relationship. </li>
            <li> Isabela de la Fuente --- A model student and trans woman whose secret is publicly exposed. </li>
            <li> Luis Navarro --- A quiet, artistic student who becomes a target of bullying. </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section id="reviews" class="section">
        <h2>Reviews</h2>
        <p>"This is a very good show with a very interesting plot. I can totally see something like this happening in todays world. Where everyone has their dirty and untold secrets on their phone and all it takes to bring it to light is a hacker." - Natalia</p>
